{"tid":2029244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港元銀行同業拆息全線上升","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T09:41:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8cad52d839ea9f2d7877df9cf737757e73e473fb","tid":2029244,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"港元銀行同業拆息全線上升<br />\n22.05.2020 14:30<br />\n<br />\n港元匯率波動，昨日人大審議香港國安法草案的消息傳出後，港匯曾回落至兩星期低位，現報7.7528兌一美元。而港元折息全線上升，隔夜息由0.12071厘升至0.34167厘，一星期拆息由0.3厘升至0.863厘，用作按息基準的一個月拆息由0.628厘，升至近1.019厘。<br />\n<br />\n長期息方面，三個月拆息由1.056厘升至近1.289厘，六個月拆息由1.294厘升至1.383厘，十二個月拆息由1.449厘升至1.532厘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289383&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289383%26csid%3D261_368&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5aed31bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289383&amp;csid=261_368</a>"},{"pid":"e753e575f8770191090b0493079c8087716db798","tid":2029244,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"依家先轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d8a93d98b7b0e3fbe26e57dfb8499fd283819d","tid":2029244,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"有無人懷疑<br />\n某銀行裡面都有詐騙集團線眼<br />\n例如有人過了一筆錢去你戶口<br />\n嗰幾日就會有好多不知明詐騙集團電話黎搵你。"}]}